These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, writer, social-worker, paramedic
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, rat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, october, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the social-worker is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the paramedic is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the pilot is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Job    | writer  | paramedic | social-worker    | pilot       |
| Pet         | lizard | rat    | mouse      | chinchilla |
| Birthday   | september   | october | june | august        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
There are 4 different nationalities: german, american, dutch, japanese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, comedy, romance, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is the german##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| Nationality         | american | dutch | japanese | german |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | scientific   | romance     | time-travel      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, almond-milk, iced-tea
City: san-francisco, rome, boston, colone
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person traveling to boston##1
5. the russian is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | juice | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| City   | colone       | rome    | san-francisco | boston     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

