.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, cat, lizard, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, disco, d&b, trance
1. the owner of the lizard is the fan of trance##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of trance##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Pet         | hedgehog | bird | lizard | cat |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Music-Genre   | disco | jazz         | trance      | d&b        |

