.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, software-developer, social-worker, pilot
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, strawberry, peach, corn
1. the software-developer is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the person eating watermelon is the social-worker##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the software-developer##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| Job   | social-worker  | nurse        | pilot  | software-developer       |
| Food         | watermelon | peach    | strawberry | corn |

