.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, ivory, emerald, coral
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, motorbike, tram
1. the person who likes yellow is the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the person who likes coral is the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Color           | ivory | emerald | coral | yellow |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Transport   | tram   | taxi     | motorbike | snowmobile       |

