.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, snooker, whist
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, ritmeester, pall-mall, tiparillo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is the person playing snooker##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
8. the ritmeester-smoker is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Game          | backgammon  | whist | snooker   | scrabble     |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | ritmeester   | vegafina  | pall-mall |
| Movie-Genre   | spy         | disaster  | mystery | thriller  |

