.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, cycling, climbing, swimming
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, blend, siglo, chaman
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the siglo-smoker##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the chaman-smoker is the person drinking juice##1
7. the blend-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | juice     | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Sport   | swimming  | water-polo | climbing       | cycling    |
| Cigar   | blend   | chaman | bolivar    | siglo |

