.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, lily, balloon-flower, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, jazz, punk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, august, june, march
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growslily##1
5. the person who growslily is on the right of the fan of punk##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Flower          | balloon-flower        | bellflower   | lily  | amaryllis   |
| Music-Genre   | blues         | punk     | d&b    | jazz       |
| Birthday         | august | october | june | march |

