There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, tomato, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, collecting, writing, gardening
1. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | snowmobile | subway | bike        |
| Food       | zucchini | pumpkin  | spinach | tomato     |
| Hobby        | collecting    | writing   | gardening  | puzzles |

