.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle, fish, ferret
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, folk, house, classical
1. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of folk##1
6. the fan of techno is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the fan of house##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Pet         | hedgehog  | ferret | turtle  | fish |
| Sport       | volleyball | rugby        | weightlifting | cricket       |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | folk          | classical          | house       |

