2. the person who growslily is the person who likes mauve##1
3. the spanish is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes white##1
6. the person who likes purple is the pakistani##1
7. the spanish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color         | white   | blue   | purple | mauve |
