.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, jet-ski, motorbike, boat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, metal, rock, trance
House: cape-cod, victorian, gothic-revival, modern
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the gothic-revival house is the fan of trance##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the modern house##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Transport         | boat | jet-ski    | van        | motorbike |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock     | trance        | blues   |
| House         | victorian   | cape-cod | gothic-revival | modern  |

