.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, accountant, librarian, chef
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, photography, singing, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the librarian##1
2. the librarian is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is the chef##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the doctor is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job      | doctor        | chef    | accountant | librarian      |
| Hobby   | fishing        | dancing   | photography  | singing  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball | soccer   | climbing |

