3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the colonial house is the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the wooden house##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the wooden house##1
7. the wooden house is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
