3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | reading | dancing | magic-tricks | filmmaking |
| Sport         | cycling | basketball | tennis  | rowing  |
| City     | miami  | paris | hannover     | liverpool  |

