4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the indonesian is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Pet           | rabbit  | horse  | lizard | rat |
| Nationality   | russian   | indonesian | nigerian   | pakistani      |
| City         | prague | san-francisco    | miami   | marseilles         |

 